 editor you can download many mission files for endless gameplay these missions can include heli races races combat missions skill building missions modded missions and many more the realism in the game ranging from the bullet drop bullet damage the ai and aircraft flight all of these and more if what creates an amazing game overall i recommend this game to anyone with the money and a pc that will be able to run the game with at least medium graphics running at 30fps or more
