arma 3 is a wonderfully developed title from bohemia i can honestly say it is one of my all time pc favourites it comes with full campaign map editor multiplayer modes great mods a fantastic and active community yes this game truly offers it all i would genuinley recommend this to anyone from the casual mess around gamer to the most hardcore military simulation fan this game is all around fun you can use features such as the map editor to create realistic raids battles and live scenarios or simply use it to fly around in shoot at people or have yourself a nice little airshow this game also has a fantastic control system truly giving you full control of your camera view player movement weapons and vehicles i would also recommend this especially to anyone who enjoyed arma 2 this is a perfect successor with more features more mods and my favourite improvement the animations if youre like me then you wouldnt have enjoyed some parts of arma 2 because the animations were dodgy glitchy and didnt always work quite right however youll love to know that these animation issues have been massively improved in arma 3 the animations work smoothly and look great doing it from scrambling inout of a jet to weapon recoil and player animations its all been fixed and now works at its true best to show everyone what the arma series is really like conclusion i would most definitley recommend this game to anyone casuals sim fans and all this game has the full package and is well worth the asking price and that cant be said for all games these days you get it all in one purchase so do yourself a favour and buy it i dont like using numbers but if i had to it would get a 9810 from me 
