arma 3 a tacticool shooter sorry that was terrible arma 3 is an apparent military simulator id personally call it a casual simulator considering the bugs the engine is riddled with them but the devs are active on fixing bugs and creating new ones in the process there are issues such as  the movement system transitions can be jarring a sprint can becoming a walk just because the terrain is slightly steeper which has got me killed more than a few times in the past though it can be solved by running in weird ways up hills  over zealous stamina system 60lb of equipment will drain your stamina whilst jogging in a few minutes 10lb will do so in a few seconds later and issues like that the guys i play with tend to disable it and for good reason  futuristic theme through the use of various real world vehicles and weapons  no aks m416s and countless other classic weapons we all know and love sucks in my opinion  really dumb ai some improvements over the arma 2 ai  ai reacts faster and better but can react a little overzealous a single soldier in a good position can lock up squads by taking random shots preventing them from being ordered around units love to crawl when under fire requiring a lot of micromanaging as a squad leader  if youre playing as zeus or using high command for squads good luck there are many others but i cant think of them at the moment but now for some good news you can install mods fixing a large number of gameplay related issues sadly the first issue with the movement system cant be fixed or hasnt at least but the stamina system has been fixed by a number of mods to be somewhat more realistic and more managable mods such as rhs escalation the us forces and russian armed forces parts plus the hlc packs solve the lack of modern weapons  the two mods  packs are my faviourites for this sort of thing various realism mods around such as agm and cse also help improve the realism of the game dlc is also free with the game sort of similar to what they did in arma 2 you get the content but with some restrictions  so you can play with people who have it though you may not be able do access all the features and there may be some annoying notifications p
