this game looks gorgeous on ultra settings and is great for benchmarking this game requires a hefty rig to run stable 60fps 1080p which is a big factor on whether you take a risk on purchasing the game if you have a low end system the multiplayer is very cpu intensive and could lead to unexpected drops of frames even on the most beefy of pcs this game however is packed with singleplayer content and a large variety of multiplayer modes the game also features a mission editor so you can make your own missions or download them off the steam workshop with the peformance issues in mind this still is an amzing game and is worth a fullprice purchase if you have friends which can play with you on it 910 great game but lowmedium end rigs or even pcs with a not great cpu be weary
