great game great mods great community this game has so many possibilities i couldnt even give you an estimated guess the pseudorealism in this game is absolutely fantastic and can make for some pretty clever shenanigans when put to the test with modern graphics gameplay mechanics and a hearty helping of good although somewhat overpriced dlc it definitely has a top spot contender in my book in single player the campaign missions are beautifully paced something which we rarely see in this genre while playing them i felt very engaged and felt a very present sense of urgency this sense of urgency really helps to propel the first chapter because you feel as if the world around you is slipping away right as you and your comrades fight to take it back on top of that there are some very interesting mechanics and side missions you can do during the campaign one of which will let you do a sort of freeroam mode where you can complete various usergenerated missions these missions will pop up out of nowhere as you are running along on your atv deep into enemy territory as you suddenly come upon a military checkpoint with heavy armaments you can either choose to systematically take the sentries and those pesky lmg carrying grunts or you can choose to rush right in and take it for mother russia but you could also just run around it seeing as how you have an atv but alas how much fun would that be this game has some of the best gamemodes and usercreated mods that i have ever had the pleasure of playing and competing in with such smashhit game modes as wasteland king of the hill just to name a few and my personal favorite breaking point the fun almost never stops however i did definitely have the most fun on breaking point a dayz esque master piece with a beautiful blend of pvp and pve battling zombies is not as cumbersome as they may be to a lowgear player in dayz and i think it for the better when you have low level gear they are just something to avoid as you survey the outskirts of town on the large 300km map altis or the many other maps that the mod offers while playing with a group on this mod as well as other gamemodes i have had some of the best online gaming experiences i have ever had and thats hard to beat allinall i think that this is a musthave for anybody who loves to play with a group of friends on a saturday night and have fun killing a bunch of noobs militarystyle
