been playing this game for about 8 months now and thought id publish my review of this game when i first started to play the game i was new to arma so didnt know the controls it was quite tricky to figure out all the different controls but after a week or 2 i got to grips with most of it if you like real battles and the strategy of it then i would buy this game you will enjoy it very much the game is more in depth compared to other games like battlefield for example its more realistic which is why i started playing it the graphics in game look amazing and the way they made the maps are very good also so if you have a good graphics card you will see the benefit on high settings the best thing about the game is there is many different mods you can play which i never realised before but ive had so much fun playing different ones really you are buying this game but getting several of them for free as the mods are totally different to the others but still the same weapons and such but it feels different in how you play so buying it is very worth while its mainly all i play its that good
