sgt jackson 310515 final entry stranded we have been caught in a bitter fire fight lasting over 2 days ambushed as we attempted to flee from the island by an elite infantry unit we sort refuge in an old farm house my men and i fought bravely holding back the enemy contact to hq has proved fruitless they have abandoned the island and the few soldiers that remain my thoughts in this quiet period turn to family and friends back home my lovely wife and two twin boys if they somehow get this journal i want them to know i love them dearly i cannot dwell too long i can hear the enemy i hold back the tears to keep face in front of my men we have seen that the enemy do not take prisoners of war in fact they make an example of captured soldiers in a truly horrific manner when captured you are stripped of your items and forced into a vehicle drove by the ai the driver is given a way point from one end of altis to the other you are not allowed to leave the vehicle or drive the vehicle yourself they are barbarians my men and i are down to our last rounds of ammunition i myself only have my side arm we know we will not survive the next assault i have thought about saving one round for myself but i dont want those s out there to have that kind of satisfaction my engineer kevin a brave man with a mustache worthy of a medal on its own merit he approached me and told me he has one explosive charge left we discuss our options knowing full well our situation kevin johnson taylor and i have decided the last man standing will detonate the charge we will go down fighting to the last the charge is set im not a religious man but if there is a god may he have mercy on our souls i hear the enemies battle cry farewell despite the occasional clumsy ai this game is that realistic just fantastic buy it now
