a tactical sim that only has aspects of a game arma iii is not intended to be a game it does not have the action most are used to from todays millitary shooter genre what it does have it has in spades a deep simulation environment that spans accross some of the largest landscape to be placed in a title thus far a plethora of weapons and set ups allow for equipping the perfect blend of survival and attack the ability for user made content to be easily added to the base of the files adds for creativity and fun arma iii is a title that asks you to make your own fun it will not be for everyone and even those who may enjoy camping out with a sniper rifle for hours on end may find it dry and cumbersome however if you are looking for one of the more realistic takes on millitary shooters arma iii will have what you are looking for even if it doesnt it gives you the tools to make it
